@124=~"I have the tails you asked for. Here they are."~
@125=~"I've got a whole collection of tails here. They're rather tangly but I hope you can work with that."~
@126=~"Nice little trinket. Got anything for sale?"~
@127=~"I shall leave you alone, then. Goodbye."~
