@129=~"I have the tails you asked for. Here they are."~
@130=~"I've got a whole collection of tails here. They're rather tangly but I hope you can work with that."~
@131=~"Nice little trinket. Got anything for sale?"~
@132=~"I shall leave you alone, then. Goodbye."~
@133=~"Tell me something about yourself. What are you doing in Sigil?~